scripts.export_key: PT Integration A: Set Custom Fields
scripts.name: PT Integration A: Set Custom Fields
scripts.script_text:
# Set fields

incident.properties.pt_int_num_artifacts = rule.properties.num_artifacts
incident.properties.pt_int_num_runs = rule.properties.num_runs
incident.properties.pt_int_delay = rule.properties.delay
incident.properties.pt_int_sample_data = rule.properties.sample_data.content
scripts.description:
Sets the fields:
- pt_int_num_artifacts
- pt_int_num_runs
- pt_int_delay
- pt_int_sample_data

automations.scripts_to_run: PT Integration A: Set Custom Fields

functions.display_name: PT Integration A: Process Added Artifact

description.content: Processes the Artifact added. Just returns a success = True

functions.name: pt_integration_a_process_added_artifact

workflows.name: PT Integration A: Process Added Artifact

description.content:
Function that:
- Sleeps for delay
- Generates list of num_artifacts
- Returns list of Artifacts to add, remaining number of runs and sample data

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><definitions xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:resilient="http://resilient.ibm.com/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" targetNamespace="http://www.camunda.org/test"><process id="pt_integration_a_run" isExecutable="true" name="PT Integration A: Run"><documentation/><startEvent id="StartEvent_155asxm"><outgoing>SequenceFlow_0tn4bhc</outgoing></startEvent><serviceTask id="ServiceTask_0mtbc8n" name="PT Integration A: Run" resilient:type="function"><extensionElements><resilient:function uuid="fe2fb2c7-b522-4874-b898-8f5c86a667e8">{"inputs":{},"post_processing_script":"
results_content = results.content

# Add all Artifacts
for a in results_content.artifacts_to_create:
  
  artifact_description = u"{0}\n\n{1}".format(a.description, results_content.sample_data)
  
  incident.addArtifact("String", a.value, artifact_description)
  
# Update num_runs
incident.properties.pt_int_num_runs = results_content.remaining_runs","pre_processing_script":"
inputs.pt_int_num_artifacts = incident.properties.pt_int_num_artifacts
